<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/4" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="" width="" class="close-credits" style="height:2em;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>SCP-5353：</strong>有人记得Fritz Obermeyer吗？<br />
<strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3337265&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1609921832" alt="Tufto" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3337265)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tufto" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3337265); return false;">Tufto</a></span>。这篇故事属于<a href="/the-man-who-wasnt-there-hub">乌有之人</a>设定，且是“没有人会赢”队在<a href="/canon-renaissance-contest">设定复兴竞赛</a>的第四篇参赛作品。 更多Tufto的作品可在<a href="/tufto-personnel-file">这里</a>找到。<br />
<strong>图源：</strong> 图片裁切自一张CC0/公有领域照片，可在<a href="https://pxhere.com/en/photo/142044">这里</a>找到。</p>
</div>
<hr />
<div class="credit-back" style="text-align: center;">
<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/credit:backmodule/code/2" align="" frameborder="" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="height:2em;width: 100%;margin: 0;padding: 0;border: 0;background: transparent;"></iframe></p>
</div>
